== SOURCE

https://ocula.com/magazine/art-news/google-reconstructs-lost-klimt-paintings-with-ai/

== AGENT

Google Arts & Culture

== GOAL

Recolour lost works from painter Gustav Klimt.

== DATA

They had images of Klimt’s surviving coloured artworks, as well as thousands of images of other art to learn things like object boundaries and textures.

== METHODS

Supervised.

== RESULTS

The paintings were given colour.

== ISSUES

People may see issues with recreating a dead artist's work.

== SCORE

7

== COMMENTS

I think it’s very interesting that a machine learning algorithm can learn to recolour artwork in such an accurate way.
